{"tid":2272210,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"送UberEats沒穿內衣！混血妹激凸爆紅…起底是辣模","createTime":"2020-11-05T02:53:14.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-05T05:12:15.000Z","uid":147522,"like":2,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"a89eab006448e29eecefb0cd48a8bfbdbd180681","tid":2272210,"uid":147522,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T02:53:14.000Z","msg":"外送行業興起，不少年輕人都投入這項行業，日本近日更出現一位火辣的美女外送員，送餐時僅穿著半截小可愛，小蠻腰跟馬甲線一覽無遺，還疑似沒穿內衣激凸，讓人看得鼻血狂噴，經過一陣肉搜，原來這位正妹竟是位專業模特兒。<br />\n<br />\n日本節目《アノ人なんなん》在近日採訪到一位Uber Eats辣妹外送員瑪麗亞羽（マリア友），及肩金髮跟深邃的混血五官，寬大外套下是緊身小可愛，大方秀出小蠻腰跟結實腹肌，最令人驚訝的是這位辣妹疑似沒穿內衣，渾圓胸型跟胸前兩點都被看光，讓現場來賓眼睛都不知道要放哪裡，主持人還語帶讚嘆地說：「最好的隆起。（最高の隆起）」。<br />\n<br />\n其實瑪麗亞羽是日本、西班牙和菲律賓的三國混血兒，現年26歲的她是專業的模特兒，還是中國某時尚雜誌的專屬日籍模特兒，可說是小有名氣，沒想到如今會在日本當外送員爆紅，引起日網上一陣騷動。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kXMto7j.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkXMto7j.jpg&h=0e723dfa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/gDvU37k.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FgDvU37k.jpg&h=471117b3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Qy8fOy0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQy8fOy0.jpg&h=cee38e00&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vKHwmT1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvKHwmT1.jpg&h=bee12804&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"312e6b90f08b176fac923c26efb34d5fd3ae1ef2","tid":2272210,"uid":2746,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T02:59:50.000Z","msg":"10"},{"pid":"84839286dca5fa7edc3f937bd1329a67bbd321bc","tid":2272210,"uid":367518,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T03:09:05.000Z","msg":"9"},{"pid":"fffe0ae79a43a3163aaf7e36a94433f0f0b3e9a3","tid":2272210,"uid":122134,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-05T03:12:35.000Z","msg":"8"},{"pid":"a087b07e7b4fdd4f181b458e1e124aa48ec00a9c","tid":2272210,"uid":182888,"like":0,"disl